<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.5.6">
<l>maṉicaru maṟṟu muṟṟumāy māyap piṟavi piṟanta</l>
<l>taṉiyaṉ piṟappili taṉṉait taṭaṅkaṭal cērnta pirāṉaik</l>
<l>kaṉiyaik karumpiṉiṉ cāṟṟaik kaṭṭiyait tēṉai yamutai</l>
<l>muṉiviṉṟi yēttik kuṉippār muḻutuṇar nīrmai yiṉārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The solitary one who took miraculous births as humans, others</l>
<l>and everything, the one without birth, the lord who joined the vast icean,</l>
<l>the ripe fruit, the sweet sap of sugarcan, the sweetmeat, the honey</l>
<l>– those who bow endlessly praising him are of the nature to understand all.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
